I"±<p>When the <em>Firewall</em> is enabled in Hetzner Robot, outgoing TCP connections wonâ€™t work until they are explicitly allowed by this rule:</p>

<ul>
  <li>Name: <code class="highlighter-rouge">TCP_Out</code></li>
  <li>Source IP: <code class="highlighter-rouge">0.0.0.0/0</code></li>
  <li>Destination IP: <code class="highlighter-rouge">0.0.0.0/0</code></li>
  <li>Destination port: <code class="highlighter-rouge">32768-65535</code></li>
  <li>Protocol: <code class="highlighter-rouge">tcp</code></li>
  <li>TCP flags: <code class="highlighter-rouge">ack</code></li>
  <li>Action: <code class="highlighter-rouge">accept</code></li>
</ul>

